org.openspml.v2.util.xml
Class ReflectiveXMLMarshaller

java.lang.Object
  org.openspml.v2.util.xml.ReflectiveXMLMarshaller
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLMarshaller
public class ReflectiveXMLMarshaller
extends java.lang.Object
implements XMLMarshaller

This class works in concert with the implementations of in the msg.subpackages to marshall the values there into XML. We use a protocol for field names that make this possible. This was more expedient than hand coding the marshalling, but may not be as performant as one would like.

Author:
kent.spaulding@sun.com

Date: Feb 9, 2006
